channel.title: Teleports Don't light up? [Delta]
channel.description: Not a huge problem, i just think it would make my server look nicer if i could figure out how to make all the custom teleport spells in the spellbook light up. (such as varrock is my home tele) The spells all require no runes and no skill level required to cast them so why don't they light up? can't seem to figure it out. Help please
